      <body>
         <head>To <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers0763.xml"/>Samuel Furly</persName></head>
         <opener><placeName>Tullamore</placeName><lb/><date when="1758-05-01">May 1, 1758</date><lb/><lb/>
            <salute>Dear Sammy,</salute>
         </opener>
         <p>Two conversations I have had with the <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers0105.xml"
               />Bishop of Londonderry</persName>,<note place="foot" n="1">The Bishop of Derry since
                  <date when="1747">1747</date> had been <persName><ptr
                     target="/persons/pers0105.xml"/>William Barnard</persName> (<date from="1679"
                  to="1768">1697â€“1768</date>). <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers2180.xml"
                  />JW</persName> was consulting <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers0105.xml"
                  />Barnard</persName> about the possibility of <persName><ptr
                     target="/persons/pers0763.xml"/>Furly</persName> being ordained without
               requirement of a title (see the letter of <date when="1758-04-08">Apr. 8</date>
               above).</note> and <foreign rend="italic">processimus pulchre</foreign>.<note
               place="foot" n="2">&apos;We are proceeding well.&apos;</note> I intend to write to
                  <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers0105.xml"/>him</persName> in a few days, and
            then I shall be able to form a better judgement. <persName><ptr
                  target="/persons/pers0105.xml"/>He</persName> loves the Methodists from his heart.
            But <persName><ptr target="/persons/pers0105.xml"/>he</persName> is not free from the
            fear of man. Yet I have much hope that love will conquer fear. Will it not conquer all
            sin?</p>
         <p>Why do you not go every afternoon to visit the sick? Can you find a more profitable
            employment? I am,</p>
         <p/>
         <closer><signed>Your affectionate brother,<lb/><persName>J.
            Wesley</persName></signed></closer>
      </body>
